### ============================================================
### 디바이스 토큰 관리 APIs (Push Notification)
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 디바이스 토큰 등록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/device-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "fcmToken": "fcm-device-token-here",
  "deviceType": "ANDROID",
  "deviceModel": "Galaxy S24",
  "osVersion": "14"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 디바이스 토큰 해제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/device-tokens?fcm_token=fcm-device-token-here
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 모든 디바이스 토큰 해제 (로그아웃)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/device-tokens/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 등록된 토큰 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/device-tokens
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 배지 카운트 초기화 (앱 접속 시 호출)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/device-tokens/badge/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
